isFinishedWithDocument

public boolean isFinishedWithDocument(DocText docText)
Determine whether this extractor is finished processing the doc texts's document.

At this level, this returns true if stopAtFirst and didFirst.

NOTE: Subclasses should extend this with any other criterea for being finished with a document.
